data.description: Pender Woods at Cane Bay is a new community now offering this Supernova plan by Starlight Homes. The Supernova is 2 story with 5 bedrooms, 3 baths and an open concept layout. This home is situated on a large homesite. Quick Close! Pender Woods at Cane Bay is centrally located between Summerville and Moncks Corner. Pender Woods has all the conveniences the low country has to offer. With close proximity to Lake Moultrie, Lake Marion, Cypress Garden Plantation, Azalea Park, Hutchinson Square and a short drive to downtown Charleston and the beaches you can spend your days and nights enjoying an abundance of activities or just relaxing poolside.
